ox's speed limitations.\", \"thinkingSignature\": \"{\\\"id\\\":\\\"rs_04c3cf33d95e4f3d0169fc284f5dc8819c88b749e83a00480a\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"reasoning\\\",\\\"encrypted_content\\\":\\\"gAAAAABp_Chg3OTNCavr-D8fNr92rL-ZMx44DQcP3gAZZ7fXBll5yM7GbVgfTC7Z5jQ6gFeQMqPwdohxiyad_DPDHispX9Vfndk8FCEEKKHpaI3QoDtGuzErggyro3C2TqqqIwQLj5KiRiYRkhEK78ssTWJchKKbSB-Khyuzok1B4PcXLR4B46lGYG6Y-J4Ucg9PKXhcGyMaM873SGjRfdi-pfzEhWvTYUrfSiZq-LAbIHAOjpRlk-Ki0sM9cwExfDDPL1d0PtpK5vz8XJgO0qz273c8E3xaq2t8xY2xxwZ29iIHrHJ_jB2b0VtVXYbmKtIe9i2ZjcEEMLG_jxczwTAY9-kw4YLMTqgVcfSicBDoUnflPXGalbOw6OTcTT0yRJLWOpj1UDlHSWFShnr0vvoZ46ZY9FX7w-5tJDh_B7Jj_tjvGFaUbWfL8VZ-UVz1EeBeWePunM3TFNMWqG3zQjZFnC_fvPEJchBV2drqFJTgfqwgTQpVhVuzdnXCw42oUR8l8XR0gaytaXPC7pG7yqh5i2j0ulgHk9h9GPQMvpJW4wYFLEiokTTqvA5vy1Naqdp3QAssO-1fHPwJHME1jWOXVh-GXuXo1HHRXtdTxUJz5Ax2RdrM3hNIO4Ae1mYH2ol0D5liPSXqCu-R7LFEAag2UyYAp7OvuqJEivg0qeN2Q70u2kR0xmJkgNrjb-R-RbamRL0BT8z0olWbgkHysGNLGmBkTRlYQshUC9O_ezaHDSp-Cqa2Ug9TlZT1Y8OsfZNfxwNnYbh_s-FvuTPmlfDoXVnjjoQkm8CevWpfoSAHTCszWWHtlJusBIEJgqAQYyUurhKT5LGQsL9Ufwzs1fF1ZG9FHslWc47kFe-xctdTBz1D28r3MD4C4VK6zkRFmkxQMXG7ox5fFp1_b3vovYpcyKn3zcvJZM4dEQ-76eeb3ZtH00OCyjvweExtmmbm_2nPWs_trUwJdSWN94obX7BOHTId9S_NpSYhKuXXRothW5192iRzyZc3Zi0XnTFTna4Lu8FrBZXg0v_WGtIXmmwdXkpcvLr40nYiKl-9xOl8sxzkGf6tQCUpcu3WWD2jHoiFBN9FqmxwHDNxQlzOrRnhDnZBZDn5M2Gqcb53TWBWoHwhy8O-0igaIr7TyYjKcRdpPG6uJXHf3a3li2_iKk3iChZ0-LGA9qApERdEeJw_O1HPE3hWWV6SrxEK0MrXiY3lLYulS0bYhgoyJLKqmAmS4QXfzKnHmt3gG-QPaz1qUfEg7r5tGzQBWpioeqPb-Q4XqexuUhAbI32uBygRE1iP0Bkny0kA_u_lL-McQVptWvri9BZlMB1xB5loowdmIhmrDasNOUfaTvncjIABQRCsPRA6X9J4466lIidOKZtxXNlK1KbR0LlziljhgqdZBgibcRWzLrjqgu_JJNPMFqROtfGJUM8dAub7wz8bxRjdEGbwO1u3F35Pap5nrnbbAssCvqoNy62ImVlm9S3Fecf9U6A7Pzx-kf_M1hhd-4-TmbntqDFFHbPmvMSdeG7HDhFm1Evb8BzdVx-xWdgMfEKshyWZ1eeYMxaIJATvJs8gQlnHrxHxmXbR43fPFjxc5pdnWCxMJI0CzKwXHOz9pnDWeMqazLc4LUsgR164Aw_Y0PHYDc62XzzxYgkafFR7l7BxPYK3nk0lBwwlDNYPW5Z7SoRRhhl3PILNYnt5iFlUB0a-aEO7ME_lWOWAsf9ICGWQJAYwRXBNuqzpYZC60MrjwzbhebwZ7hCFmStU0A86vDEKHxQpWi5tSwFrQxGmrjz8ssZjdrK7bA3DSsRqI